item.title: Eden Project Question 6
item.description: To what extent did The Eden Project benefit from the time spent on its budgeting? (16 marks) The Eden Project produced a large, detailed budget based on information that they had researched, allowing them to easily approach investors with a plan, showing what they were doing and how they planned to achieve it.
